02:44.964 --> 02:45.829
It's some sort of
family emergency.

02:45.831 --> 02:48.031
What, her family found
out she works at Hooters?

02:48.766 --> 02:50.166
Why do you always
have to put her down?

02:50.467 --> 02:51.600
Maybe it's
because I can't walk

02:51.602 --> 02:53.001
from here to the corner without

02:53.003 --> 02:54.402
running into eight
guys she's fucked.

02:55.804 --> 02:56.970
Bye.

02:57.504 --> 02:59.805
Honey, I was just-- Oh!
Watch the suit, watch the suit.

02:59.807 --> 03:01.773
Just kidding, it's
a joke, come on.

03:01.775 --> 03:03.007
Don't be so serious.

03:04.609 --> 03:05.675
I love you.

03:07.778 --> 03:09.411
-I love you!
-Bye, bye.

03:09.645 --> 03:10.811
Bye, bye!

03:10.813 --> 03:12.546
Bye, bye, bye, bye, bye!

03:17.785 --> 03:19.685
-Hey.
-Hey.

03:24.790 --> 03:25.890
Yo!

03:26.091 --> 03:27.191
Hey.

03:27.525 --> 03:28.691
What's up?

03:28.693 --> 03:29.925
What's up?

03:29.927 --> 03:31.259
I ordered you a drink.

03:31.261 --> 03:32.860
Good, I need one.

03:33.161 --> 03:35.662
-Coming.
-Hey, Zach.

03:35.963 --> 03:37.530
-Hey, Bryce!
-What's up, man?

03:37.532 --> 03:38.664
How's it goin'?

03:38.666 --> 03:39.631
All right, how long's it been?

03:39.633 --> 03:40.832
It's been a while.

03:40.834 --> 03:42.533
