03:54.507 --> 03:55.572
Yeah.

03:55.973 --> 03:57.106
You know that line
between being a drinker

03:57.108 --> 03:58.507
and being an alcoholic?

03:58.509 --> 03:59.608
Mm-hm.

03:59.610 --> 04:01.009
