out of that line.

04:03.179 --> 04:04.278
Wow, sorry to hear that, man.

04:04.280 --> 04:05.579
No. Hey, it's cool. I'm good.

04:05.780 --> 04:07.213
So I hear congratulations
are in order?

04:07.215 --> 04:08.280
You're getting married.

04:08.282 --> 04:09.314
I'm getting married.

04:09.316 --> 04:10.348
Wow.

04:10.350 --> 04:12.416
Yes.
How 'bout you?

04:12.950 --> 04:14.483
No, no, I've
been seeing someone

04:14.485 --> 04:16.418
