but nothing serious.

04:16.652 --> 04:18.152
-To Matthew.
-Yep.

04:18.154 --> 04:19.253
To Matt.

04:20.488 --> 04:21.588
Can't believe he's dead.

04:22.790 --> 04:25.024
Getting run over by a
bus in broad daylight?

04:25.325 --> 04:26.458
What are the odds?

04:26.959 --> 04:28.459
When it's your time,
it's your time.

04:29.127 --> 04:30.393
That's life,
one minute you're walking

04:30.395 --> 04:32.661
down the street,
next minute-- Bam!

04:32.663 --> 04:34.496
Pulling your skull
fragments outta

04:34.498 --> 04:36.431
the front grill
of the city bus.

04:36.799 --> 04:38.966
I'm not so sure that
it was an accident.

04:40.902 --> 04:42.102
What the fuck does that mean?

04:42.837 --> 04:45.104
