me a couple weeks ago.

04:46.072 --> 04:48.973
He was depressed,
he was incoherent.

04:49.207 --> 04:50.874
And he thought he
was being followed.

04:51.342 --> 04:52.575
You know what,
and then he told me

04:52.809 --> 04:54.242
he had been outta
work since January,

04:54.476 --> 04:55.876
and that he was flat broke now.

04:56.143 --> 04:57.810
So, anyway, Matt's getting
harassed by creditors.

04:58.178 --> 04:59.511
So he asks you for money.

04:59.513 --> 05:00.912
No, no, he knows
I don't have it.

05:01.580 --> 05:02.780
