it four ways, you know?

09:38.689 --> 09:41.223
Um, that way we,
you know, would be,

09:41.225 --> 09:43.124
equal partners, you know?

09:43.992 --> 09:46.393
Uh. On principal
whatever you pay back,

09:46.395 --> 09:48.061
plus some accrued interest,
but,

09:48.063 --> 09:51.330
you know, this, I mean this
is how it works, right?

09:51.332 --> 09:52.397
You know?

09:53.065 --> 09:56.333
